Package org.svvrl.goal.core.comp

Class AbstractOnTheFlyContainment<T>

java.lang.Object
org.svvrl.goal.core.AbstractAlgorithm
org.svvrl.goal.core.comp.AbstractOnTheFlyContainment<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of states in the complement of the second NBW
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.util.EventListener, Algorithm, AlgorithmListener
Direct Known Subclasses:
MSContainment.MSContainmentImpl, PitermanContainment.PitermanContainmentImpl, SafraContainment.SafraContainmentImpl, SliceContainment.SliceContainmentImpl
public abstract class AbstractOnTheFlyContainment<T>
extends AbstractAlgorithm
Test if the first NBW A is contained in the second NBW B by constructing the intersection of A and the complement of B incrementally. The search for a counterexample is performed by a double depth-first search.
Author:
Ming-Hsien Tsai
